#

Pork Schnitzel with Lemon

35 min
$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutenegg

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

German

Course:

Main

Tags:

easyquickcomfort food

Description

A crispy, golden-brown pork schnitzel served with a zesty lemon wedge for a refreshing kick.

Ingredients

  • pork loin cutlets: 4 pieces
  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2, beaten
  • bread crumbs: 2 cups
  • vegetable oil: 1/2 cup
  • lemon: 1, cut into wedges
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
